{% extends "layout.twig" %}

{% set title = "Hosting with good support" %}
{% set activeClass = 'nav_support' %}
{% set bodyClass = 'marketing contrast' %}
{#{% set hideMainCta = 1 %}#}









{% block content %}



<h1 class="m-top-xxl" style="font-size:8.2vw">
    Support as a Service
</h1>
<div class="post m-top-xl">
    <p class="type-xl">
        <b>fortrabbit hosting is different</b>. So is our support. Instead of hiding costs for support in the general fees, we separate them. Your options are:
    </p>

    <div class="row gutter-l collapse">
        <div class="half">
            <h3>
                <span class="type-thin">1.</span> Help yourself
            </h3>
            <p>
                Most clients use fortrabbit as a self-service. The Dashboard is guided and pretty self-explaining. There is an <a href="{{ help_url }}">extensive documentation</a> and as well as a growing user-to-user <a href="http://stackoverflow.com/questions/tagged/fortrabbit">community on Stack Overflow</a>.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="half">
            <h3>
                <span class="type-thin">2.</span> Get support
            </h3>
            <p>
                One-on-one dev-to-dev eye-level support directly from the engineering team. We assist you with anything from general coding problems, to deployment work-flows, to performance tuning, to life-cycle planing, to database support{#, to security audits, to customized alerting#}.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<h2 class="m-bottom-l m-top-xl type-xxl" id="support-pricing">
    Support choices
</h2>
<div class="row gutter-no collapse wrap m-top-xs">

{% include supportPricingTable %}

</div>

<div class="row gutter-l collapse tablet wrap m-top-xl">
    <div class="quarter half-t">
        <h4>
            Team access
        </h4>
        <p>
            The Pro Support are aligned with the <a href="{{ help_url }}/collaboration">collaboration features</a>. In other words: All members of your Company have access to the Professional Support.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="quarter half-t">
        <h4>
            Cancel at any time
        </h4>
        <p>
            The minimum booking period is only one month and you don't have to contact support to cancel the Professional Support.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="quarter half-t">
        <h4>
            Test for free
        </h4>
        <p>
            The first steps are always the hardest. And we like to help. So you get a 14 days free trial of technical support just by signing up.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="quarter half-t">
        <h4>
            Tailored support plans
        </h4>
        <p>
            For enterprise clients we offer even higher levels of managed service with hands-on and pro-active support. Please <a href="mailto:sales@fortrabbit.com?subject={{ "I am interested in Pro Support"|url_encode }}&body={{ "Hey rabbits,"|url_encode }}">contact us</a>.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>


